{"tid":1213692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Vox 既 Johnny Harris 同埋英國衛報 Guardian 希望示威者講下自己所見所聞感受","createTime":"2019-06-13T02:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T18:57:00.000Z","uid":36324,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a17db81880a1ee8c9d86865361b5dff3224a46ec","tid":1213692,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:25:44.000Z","msg":"Vox's Johnny Harris 即係之前黎做 Border 系列個位，希望收集大家既聲音檔案:<br />\nHong Kong! If you're participating in the protests we want to hear from you for a Vox podcast. Tell us what you're seeing. What this means for you. Why are you protesting. Send a voice memo file to worldly@vox.com<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p9WvDau.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp9WvDau.jpg&h=59b066a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國衛報 Guardian <br />\nWe would like to hear from readers in Hong Kong about the situation as you see it.<br />\n<br />\nHow do you feel about the situation? Are you taking part in the protests? If you are there now you can get in touch, anonymously if you wish, via the encrypted form below &ndash; only the Guardian has access to your contributions and we will not publish anything without your permission. One of our journalists may be in touch to discuss your contribution.<br />\n<br />\n入去用化名都可以，打低自己感受意見就 ok!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2019/jun/12/how-are-you-being-affected-by-the-hong-kong-protests \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2019%2Fjun%2F12%2Fhow-are-you-being-affected-by-the-hong-kong-protests%20&d=OjLoGj31iMtRFsPqVtgEmudFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=7fd81ae5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/world/2019/jun/12/how-are-you-being-affected-by-the-hong-kong-protests </a>"},{"pid":"701f9bb162ff1d5096d29025dc849b237468a938","tid":1213692,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:26:54.000Z","